{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-describing-people-at-work-basics/task-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 11","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pregledajmo dva grada koja si naučio do sada:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Grad</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Država</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ciudad de México</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">México</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Medellín</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombia</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Na španskom, imena gradova su takođe sopstvena imena i uvek počinju velikim slovom.</p>\n<p>Camila vežba kako da izgovori ove gradove. Slušajte zvukove i vežujte izgovor dok ne osetite da ste ugodni sa njihovim zvučanjem. Zatim, napišite njihova imena dole.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj/Slušajte zvuk i napiši/napišite imena ovih gradova ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Camila pominje gradove <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Medellín</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ciudad de México</span>, koji su u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombia</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">México</span>, respektivno.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-warm-up-describing-people-at-work-basics","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-describing-people-at-work-basics/task-11"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK, Colombia.</p>\n<p>BLANK, México.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Medellín","feedback":"<p>Ovaj grad se nalazi u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Colombia</span